changes: After the action, the screen transitions from the main settings menu to the "Back up & sync" detailed settings page. response: Tapping on the "Back up & sync" option will navigate to a new screen dedicated to backup and sync settings. This screen will likely present options to enable or disable backup and sync functionality, allow you to choose which types of media to back up, and possibly show the status of your current backup (e.g., whether it’s active, paused, or failed). You may also see options to manage backup storage locations or adjust sync preferences. The current "Off" status indicates that no data is being backed up or synced at the moment, and enabling it would initiate the process.
